title: 1. FFC Turbine Potsdam - Wikipedia
snippet: The upper right part shows football. The lower right side shows the letters "TP" which stand for "Turbine Potsdam". The club plays their home games at Karl Liebknecht Stadion in Potsdam-Babelsberg. They share this ground with the men's Regionalliga side SV Babelsberg 03.
